# Kubernetes拓扑网络

Kubernetes 集群的核心资源拓扑结构，用于运维监控和故障分析。

## 网络概览

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Entities["实体"]
        Node["Node 节点"]
        Pod["Pod 容器组"]
        Service["Service 服务"]
    end
    
    subgraph Relations["关系"]
        Node -->|包含| Pod
        Service -->|路由| Pod
    end
    
    subgraph Actions["行动"]
        Pod -.->|重启| RestartPod["restart_pod"]
        Node -.->|隔离| CordonNode["cordon_node"]
    end
```

---

# Entities

## Entity: pod

**Pod Instance** - Kubernetes 中的最小部署单元，一个或多个容器的集合

### Data Source

| Type | ID | Name |
|------|-----|------|
| data_view | d2mio43q6gt6p380dis0 | pod_info_view |

> **Primary Key**: `id` | **Display Key**: `pod_name`

### Data Properties

| Property | Display Name | Type | Description | Primary Key | Index |
|----------|--------------|------|-------------|:-----------:|:-----:|
| id | ID | int64 | Primary key | YES | YES |
| pod_name | Pod Name | VARCHAR | Pod name | | YES |
| pod_status | Pod Status | VARCHAR | Pod status (Running/Pending/Failed) | | YES |
| pod_node_name | Node | VARCHAR | Pod node name | | YES |
| pod_namespace | Namespace | VARCHAR | Pod namespace | | YES |
| pod_ip | Pod IP | VARCHAR | Pod IP address | | |
| pod_created_at | Created At | TIMESTAMP | Pod creation time | | |

### Property Override

| Property | Display Name | Index Config | Description |
|----------|--------------|--------------|-------------|
| pod_status | Status | fulltext + vector | Full-text and semantic search |
| pod_name | Pod Name | keyword + fulltext | Exact and fuzzy match |

### Logic Properties

#### pod_metrics

Pod 的监控指标，用于获取 CPU、内存、网络等实时数据。

- **Type**: metric
- **Source**: pod_metric (metric-model)
- **Description**: Pod monitoring metrics

| Parameter | Source | Binding | Description |
|-----------|--------|---------|-------------|
| id | property | id | Bind Pod primary key |
| pod_name | property | pod_name | Bind Pod name |
| instant | input | - | Instant query time |
| start | input | - | Range query start |
| end | input | - | Range query end |

#### pod_operator

Pod 的自定义算子，用于执行复杂计算逻辑。

- **Type**: operator
- **Source**: pod_operator (operator)
- **Description**: Pod custom operator

| Parameter | Source | Binding |
|-----------|--------|---------|
| operator_param1 | property | id |
| operator_param2 | property | pod_name |
| operator_param3 | input | - |

---

## Entity: node

**Node** - Kubernetes 集群中的工作节点，承载 Pod 运行

### Data Source

| Type | ID | Name |
|------|-----|------|
| data_view | d2mio43q6gt6p380disg | node_info_view |

> **Primary Key**: `id` | **Display Key**: `node_name`

### Property Override

| Property | Display Name | Description |
|----------|--------------|-------------|
| node_status | Node Status | Ready/NotReady/Unknown |

---

## Entity: service

**Service服务** - Kubernetes 服务抽象层，提供稳定的访问入口

### Data Source

| Type | ID | Name |
|------|-----|------|
| data_view | d2mio43q6gt6p380dith | service_info_view |

> **Primary Key**: `id` | **Display Key**: `service_name`

### Data Properties

| Property | Display Name | Type | Description | Primary Key | Index |
|----------|--------------|------|--------------|:------------:|:-----:|
| id | ID | int64 | Primary key ID | YES | YES |
| service_name | Service名称 | VARCHAR | Service名称 | | YES |
| service_namespace | 命名空间 | VARCHAR | Service所属命名空间 | | YES |
| service_type | Service类型 | VARCHAR | Service类型 (ClusterIP/NodePort/LoadBalancer) | | |
| service_cluster_ip | Cluster IP | VARCHAR | Cluster IP地址 | | |
| service_ports | 端口映射 | VARCHAR | 服务端口映射 | | |
| service_selector | Pod选择器 | VARCHAR | Pod选择器标签 | | |
| service_created_at | 创建时间 | TIMESTAMP | Service创建时间 | | |

